{"tid":2213400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美51區驚現巨大人形　UFO獵人：會動的16公尺外星機器人","createTime":"2020-09-22T13:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T16:17:43.000Z","uid":295230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d5cb5c8947e2179fe4f5bd4dbb566a20630074cd","tid":2213400,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVLGQ8T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVLGQ8T.png&h=9c1f496b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於美國內華達州的「51區」有著神秘的外星人傳言，而不明飛行物幽浮（UFO）獵人沃林（Scott C Waring）宣稱，他透過Google地球發現，51區出現一個大約16公尺高的外星機器人，並從多次觀察中認定「它會移動」。<br />\n<br />\n據《今日俄羅斯》報導，自稱擁有外星人資料庫（ET Database）的沃林，在透過Google地球（座標：37&deg;13&prime;26.26&Prime;N 115&deg;49&prime;2.37&Prime;W）瀏覽美國空軍高度機密的「51區」時，發現了這個疑似機器人的黑色人形影像，他表示，「我在51區發現了一個16公尺長的黑色人形，它的右邊似乎還有另外一個，但更短一些。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkavKt5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkavKt5.png&h=a4245d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沃林之所以認為該影像是機器人，是因為「我察看了該位置過去的圖片，發現在每張圖片裡，它會更改姿勢，所以實際上它是會動的。」除了懷疑這是一台外星機器人外，他還推測，也可能是<strong><span class=\"red\">美軍正在試驗可以用於戰鬥任務的大型機器人。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b372486113b7c184840e429af9bd5fe7dc776251","tid":2213400,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:27:35.000Z","msg":"黃容根dam"},{"pid":"0e49b6c50ddbf177c642aae6091e4d86e52cd774","tid":2213400,"uid":25601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:33:32.000Z","msg":"gun gun gundam..."},{"pid":"b00f600dbb41f3a0859e5053071418a38de50d2c","tid":2213400,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:18:40.000Z","msg":"係咪瞓緊覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642c3ddc20b0652d227c66dce37826f6efa1e225","tid":2213400,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AP0jDvs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAP0jDvs.jpg&h=10e7e660&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR1Cqas.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR1Cqas.png&h=2bd6ed94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f934eec1dec074fde63d88d919b2abc95e46a36","tid":2213400,"uid":247048,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5k5QhjXoAA3ZnJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD5k5QhjXoAA3ZnJ.jpg&h=517d972d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac7e9db7a4b2267178f3e75642fabe27879e8d8b","tid":2213400,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5QUMRXCN4CJG4GXFNIOASOV54Y.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5QUMRXCN4CJG4GXFNIOASOV54Y.jpg&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I24ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=819a5846\" target=\"_blank\">https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5QUMRXCN4CJG4GXFNIOASOV54Y.jpg</a><br />\n好彩我地中國有駱駝"},{"pid":"4f0b169140ea1b3f4827e14c9e49185926d09595","tid":2213400,"uid":137493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:24:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"706b232715198951abc4a574b7da48be00caee18","tid":2213400,"uid":19527,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5QUMRXCN4CJG4GXFNIOASOV54Y.jpg\" data-thumb